{"tid":886831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉禾創辦人鄒文懷離世 終年91歲","createTime":"2018-11-02T11:57:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T14:14:09.000Z","uid":117837,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f5211e63690b02a5e5e9e393a304c125666b5555","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:57:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181102/58868228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F58868228&d=TNc28JJvEqMuoJKdm3yFAi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=6365e137\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F58868228&h=180dca35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181102/58868228</a>"},{"pid":"454224f555a2b7a5bebc77a2e88cf93a1c8cc309","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"又一偉人殞落"},{"pid":"ffc117b50c632558515b3afd3ba2ad4d5c6e6bd9","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:58:51.000Z","msg":"嘉禾創辦人鄒文懷離世 終年91歲 友人蔡和平：個女趕去陪住佢<br />\n<br />\n嘉禾創辦人鄒文懷離世，終年91歲。《蘋果》今日中午曾致電鄒文懷女兒鄒重珩，但不獲接聽。人稱《EYT之父》的資深影視人蔡和平表示，昨日得悉鄒處於彌留階段，其女兒亦已趕到他病床旁陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n蔡稱，當年因《歡樂今宵》關係曾與鄒有數面之緣，一年前亦曾與鄒氏夫婦茶聚。他續表示，最後一次看到鄒露面，是數月前的一個派對，當時他意到鄒步履緩慢，亦需要女兒攙扶。蔡坦言，當時已感到鄒的精神和氣色不太好。<br />\n<br />\n蔡和平本身是已故武打巨星李小龍的好友，盛讚鄒文懷及嘉禾當年「將李小龍帶出世界」，更令李小龍成為香港武打演員的典範，形容他對香港電影貢獻良多，「我好respect佢。」"},{"pid":"5713097c132b88c2d407fcae5f95d3b10f41347d","tid":886831,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:59:46.000Z","msg":"港爆先兆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1be0adb89d91d38694e503ce6cf949803fd9f0","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:59:52.000Z","msg":"今年死咗幾多名人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705ad2ff6e6495cb98fb557b20d547ff7e669eb1","tid":886831,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"有無舐共、撐廿三條？"},{"pid":"ef439b5a3a01d45406c95a31c324efb80b889b6e","tid":886831,"uid":19602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:00:06.000Z","msg":"關唔關中美貿易戰事?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c13f1a837ab2ff3455db0cfdb55f9ff803fb9ea4","tid":886831,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"毛主席接見 支爆先兆"},{"pid":"00cfe60031cf5e9e7030f230af673d171c90a4bc","tid":886831,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"唔知佢有冇奶共之前唔發表任何意見<br />\n有嘅話底死<br />\n冇嘅話rip，永遠懷念"},{"pid":"d8d07bdc1511610f26c8eec5c78d10bac823215f","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"今年真係好邪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba40360d34f39449f9389df2eabcc8a1cf53e59","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bebddff60b704af9a6c4bcb7e1404c803db14cd","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"兒登小朋友連鄒文懷都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0630cd8be96b5a7b796cd2e39db39b0a4a36bb22","tid":886831,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3bebddff60b704af9a6c4bcb7e1404c803db14cd","tid":886831,"uid":117837,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"兒登小朋友連鄒文懷都唔識<img src=